input.prompt: Generate a high-quality interior design walkthrough video using the attached images as the reference, first and last frame represents the same room. The camera should smoothly pan and rotate to showcase the entire room from multiple angles, including wide shots, corner perspectives, and overhead views. Emphasize the spatial layout, furniture placement, lighting, and textures. Maintain realistic proportions and consistent design elements throughout the video. The walkthrough should feel immersive and cinematic, with natural transitions between viewpoints.
